solPicker.job
Class JobFactory

java.lang.Object
  solPicker.job.JobFactory

public class JobFactory
extends java.lang.Object

A Job Factory is used to run SolPicker and complete all the Jobs assigned by the user. The class takes an XML file as a paremeter. It validates the XML file against the schema, parses the file, calls on the newly createdJob objects to produce the appropriate fastas, and prints all the different multi-fasta sequences to different output files.

Author:
Tyler Izatt
